quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  3,78,"No e Alyahuuda en, …ďen wayliroo…ďe …óem…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen jaŇčtagol ko jeyaaka e Tawreetaare Jipporiinde nden ka Alla, fii no sikkiron ko Tawreeta …ďe woni e janngude, …óum le jeyaaka e Tawreeta, si ko woni, ko penaale e fefinadaare ma…ď…ďe e hoore Alla, hi…ďe wi'a: "Ko men jaŇčgata koo, ko ka Alla iwri", …óum le wanaa ka Alla iwri, hi…ďe ta∆īa penaale takka e Alla hara non hi…ďe anndi penaale ma…ď…ďe hoore Alla e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  3,79,"Haananaa ne…ó…óaŇčke on nde Okkata mo Deftere Jipporiinde ka Makko, O Arsike on ganndal e fahmu, O Su…ďora mo Annabaaku; refti on wi'ana yim…ďe …ďen: "Laatee jeyaa…ďe am ko woori Alla", si ko woni, yo o wi'u …ďe: "Laatee janngu…ďe golliroo…ďe ne'ira yim…ďe …ďen, mo∆ī∆īia fiyakuuji ma…ď…ďe; sabu ko jannginirton kon Deftere Jippinanaande yim…ďe …ďe, e ko laatino…óon hi…óon janngira hunnjoo fahma"."
  3,80,"Haananaa mo kadi nde o yamirta on jogitorgol Malaa'ika en e Annabaa…ďe …ďen rewetee…ďe ko woori Alla. Hara daganto mo yamirgol on yeddugol Alla …ďaawo nde won…óon jebbilanii…ďe mo?!"
  3,81,"JaŇčto an Nulaa…óo, tuma nde Alla Nanngunoo ahadi teŇčtinaandi ndin e Annabaa…ďe …ďen, O Daalani …ďe: "Nami woo no mi Okkiri on Deftere nde mi JippiŇčta e moo…óon, e fahmu mo Mi AnndiŇčta on, go…ó…óo e mo'on yottii darja woo, refti Nulaa…óo ari on immorde e Am -on woni Muhammadu jom kisiyee-, goongin…óo nden Deftere e fahmu won…óe ka moo…óon; ma on gom…óin ko o addi kon, wallito…óon mo jokkon mo. E on qirritike …óum onon Annabaa…ďe, on ∆īettii e …óum ahadi Am Tii…óundi ndin?". ∆Āe jaabii: "Men qirritike …óum". Alla Daali: "Seedanee ko'e mo'on e mofte mon, Min Mi…óo Wondi e mo'on Jeyaa…óo e Seeditanii…ďe on"."
  3,82,"Kala on …óuurnii…óo …ďaawo ndin ahadi teŇčtiniraandi seeditagol Alla e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďe; ko …ďen …óon woni yaltu…ďe e …óoftaare Alla nden."
  3,83,"E ko woori Diina kan ka O Su…ďanii jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen (Lislaamu on) woni ko …ďee yaltu…ďe e …óoftaare Alla nden …óa…ď…ďata?! Hino woodani Mo jebbilaare kala tagu wongu ka kammuuli e ka leydi, e …óoftaare -wano muumini en- maa waawneede -wano heefer…ďe …ďen-, refti ko faade ka Makko KaŇčko Alla woni ruttorde tagu ngun denndaangal; √Ďalnde Darngal fii hasbeede √Īaawee."